---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import SkillsShowcase from '@/components/SkillsShowcase.astro';

import { Picture } from 'astro:assets';
import imageWebDeveloper from '@/images/web-developer.jpg';
import imageFrontendSkills from '@/images/frontend-skills.jpg';
import imageBackendSkills from '@/images/backend-skills.jpg';
---

<Layout>
	<div class="content-wrapper bg-image">
		<div class="bg-image-wrapper" data-bg-image-overlay="8" data-bg-image-blur="1">
			<Picture src={ imageWebDeveloper } formats={['avif', 'webp']} alt="Weaving Digital Journeys" width="1920" loading="eager" />
		</div>
		<div class="row padding-500 content-text">
			<div class="col xmedium-8">
				<h1>Crafting Digital Experiences</h1>

				<p>Hi! My name is Jeremy. I am a web developer with over a decade of experience in creating stunning and functional websites!</p>
				<p>I've had the privilege of collaborating with clients from Germany and the Czech Republic and now I am looking forward to working on new projects in Spain - Madrid.</p>
				<p>Let's connect and explore how I can elevate your next project!</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="content-wrapper bg-tertiary-300">
		<div class="row content-text padding-500">
			<div class="col text-center">
				<h2>My Skill Set: A Reflection of My Passion, Curiosity, and Dedication to Learning</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="col">
				<SkillsShowcase />
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row content-text padding-top-500">
		<div class="col xxmedium-6">
			<h3>HTML, CSS, and JavaScript: The Cornerstones of Web Development</h3>

			<p>
				HTML, CSS, and JavaScript work in harmony to create the digital world we navigate daily. These three technologies form the bedrock upon which every digital experience is built.<br>
				As a web developer, I use their combined power to build functional, beautiful, and user friendly websites.
			</p>
			<p>
				Proper HTML structure ensures that each part and element of the website is easily accessible and well organized.
			</p>
			<p>
				With CSS I make sure to add colors, fonts, animations and create layouts that transform plain HTML into visually appealing design. Whether it's a sleek corporate site or a funky portfolio, CSS gives it character.
				Responsive design? No problem - CSS ensures our websites adapt gracefully to different screen sizes.
			</p>
			<p>
				Using JavaScript I can create interactive forms, build sliders, and fetch data from APIs. It's the language that turns a website into a web application.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col xxmedium-6 content-image b-shadow-bottom border">
			<div class="content-image-wrapper">
				<Picture src={ imageFrontendSkills } formats={['avif', 'webp']} alt="Crafting Web Experiences: The Trifecta of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript" width="950" class="skills-image" />
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row content-text padding-bottom-500 single-row-xxmedium">
		<div class="col xxmedium-7-12">
			<h3>PHP and MySQL: The Dynamic Duo of Web Development</h3>

			<p>
				PHP and MySQL are two powerful technologies that enable web developers to create dynamic and data-driven websites.
				Together, they form the backbone of many popular web applications, such as WordPress, Facebook, and Wikipedia.
			</p>
			<p>
				Whether it's a blog, a custom portfolio site, or a content management system, I can use both technologies to create robust and scalable web applications that deliver a great user experience and meet the specific needs of my clients.
			</p>
			<p>
				Integrating PHP with other technologies, such as HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and AJAX, allows me to create a rich and interactive web environment.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col xxmedium-1-6 content-image b-shadow-bottom border">
			<div class="content-image-wrapper">
				<Picture src={ imageBackendSkills } formats={['avif', 'webp']} alt="Powering Web Applications with PHP and MySQL" width="950" class="skills-image" />
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="content-wrapper bg-accent-300">
		<div class="row content-text padding-500">
			<div class="col">
				<h2>Web Dev Showcase: A Collection of My Projects</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="col">
				<div class="timeline">
					<div class="timeline--item" data-timeline-date="01/01/1970">
						<div class="timeline--content">
							<h3>TODO: Find archived projects</h3>
							<p>
								Voy añadiendo los proyectos poco a poco ya que los tengo que buscar en mis backups...
							</p>
						</div>
						<Picture src={ imageBackendSkills } formats={['avif', 'webp']} alt="TODO: Find archived projects" width="950" class="timeline--image" />
					</div>
					<div class="timeline--item" data-timeline-date="03/2016 - 04/2016">
						<div class="timeline--content">
							<h3>Mi primer cliente: BDK Hessen Fachverband für Kunstpädagogik</h3>
							<p>
								El primer proyecto de pago que hice para un cliente fue una página para una asociación profesional para la educación artística - BDK Hessen Fachverband für Kunstpädagogik.
							</p>
							<p>
								En esta página los estudiantes subían fotos artísticas para entrar en un sorteo y tener la oportunidad de ganar un premio.
							</p>
							<p>
								Tecnologías usadas: HTML, CSS, PHP, MySQL
							</p>
						</div>
						<Picture src={ imageBackendSkills } formats={['avif', 'webp']} alt="Mi primer cliente: BDK Hessen Fachverband für Kunstpädagogik" width="950" class="timeline--image" />
					</div>
					<div class="timeline--item" data-timeline-date="01/2016 - 06/2020">
						<div class="timeline--content">
							<h3>Programador principal en WEREKON</h3>
							<p>
								En 2016, con 16 años, fundamos con mi compañero de Alemania la agencia de publicidad WEREKON y durante los estudios de bachillerato hemos conseguido unos cuántos clientes. La idea fue mudarme a Alemania junto con mi hermano una vez que ambos termináramos los estudios. Durante los últimos 6 meses mi compañero ha encontrado pasión en otro sector laboral y nos hemos separado. Hasta el día de hoy seguimos ofreciendo soporte a los cliente que hemos adquirido durante estos 4 años.
							</p>
							<p>Dato curioso: Nuestra agencia tuvo 3 nombres diferentes - Caesar Medien, DIWERF y a finales de 2016 hemos quedado con WEREKON.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
	@include breakpoint(xmedium, down) {
		.skills-image {
			max-height: 300px;
		}
	}

	.timeline {
		position: relative;

		display: grid;
		row-gap: var(--spacer-600);

		padding-block: var(--spacer-400);

		&::before {
			content: '';

			grid-row: 1 / span -1;
			grid-column: 1 / -1;

			position: absolute;
			
			top: 0;
			left: 50%;
			transform: translateX(-50%);

			width: 2px;
			height: 100%;
			background-color: currentColor;
		}
	}

	.timeline--content {
		grid-row: 1 / -1;
		grid-column: 1 / 2;
	}

	.timeline--image {
		grid-row: 1 / -1;
		grid-column: 2 / 3;

		margin: 0 !important;

		border: 2px solid currentColor;
		border-radius: .5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-bottom);
	}

	.timeline--item {
		position: relative;

		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		align-items: center;
		column-gap: var(--spacer-400);

		&::before {
			content: '';

			position: absolute;
			top: 50%;
			left: 50%;
			transform: translate(-50%, -50%);

			width: 1.25rem;
			height: 1.25rem;
			background-color: currentColor;
			border-radius: 50%;

			z-index: 3;
		}

		&::after {
			content: attr(data-timeline-date);

			position: absolute;
			top: 50%;
			left: 50%;
			transform: translateY(-50%);

			padding: 6px 12px;
			padding-left: var(--spacer-200);

			font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
			font-size: 1.1rem;
			color: var(--color-font-primary);
			line-height: 1;

			background-color: var(--color-font-secondary);
			border-top-right-radius: 100vh;
			border-bottom-right-radius: 100vh;

			box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-right);

			z-index: 2;
		}

		&:nth-child(2n) {
			& .timeline--image {
				grid-column: 1 / 2;
			}

			& .timeline--content {
				grid-column: 2 / 3;
			}

			&::after {
				left: auto;
				right: 50%;

				padding: 6px 12px;
				padding-right: var(--spacer-200);

				border-top-left-radius: 100vh;
				border-bottom-left-radius: 100vh;
				border-top-right-radius: 0;
				border-bottom-right-radius: 0;

				box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-left);
			}
		}
	}
</style>